properties.name: spring.xcloud.component.rpc.feign.loadbalancer.random.enabled
properties.description: If true, the random load balancer for feign remote calls is enabled

properties.name: spring.xcloud.component.rpc.feign.loadbalancer.gray.enabled
properties.description: If true, the gray load balancer for feign remote calls is enabled. (If both the random load balancer and the random load balancer are enabled, only the random load balancer is enabled first)
